query: SELECT p.*, s.name as service_name, s.smshubCode, s.active as service_active, c.name as country_name, a.name as api_name FROM prices p JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa' ORDER BY p.apiId
